data.description: Contractor needed to restore this fire damaged, gutted to studs, custom built home. One-owner home built in 1981 has 4 bedrooms on main level with additional 2 bedrooms in lower level. 4.5 baths with over 3,000 sq ft. Indoor pool and walkout lower level. It is situated on 3 parcels combined totaling approximately .74 acres. Shed and small barn.
